quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,7,"Abatsokaasi bakhaba barie nende indakano ewa Nyasaye nende ewa Omurumwa wuwe, okhuyiniakhwo balia abayalakana ninabo imbeli womusikiti kwoluyali? Kho, nibabemela khubulayi, mwesi mubemele khubulayi. Toto Nyasaye yachama balia abamuritsanga."
  9,8,"Ni karie, ne nibabashila shibahenganga mwinye olwikho nohomba indakano tawe. Bakhusangasinjia butswa nende eminwa chiabu, ne emioyo chiabu chikhayile. Ne abanji mubo nibokhurula mumalako."
  9,9,"Bakusia ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye khubukusi butiti bwokhushialo, ne bekalilanga Abandu ehale nende injila yiye. Toto ni amabii muno akabakholanga."
  9,10,"Shibahenganga khubasubili olwikho nohomba indakano tawe. Abo nibo baburanga eshichelo."
  9,11,"Ne nibasaba (Nyasaye) eshileshelo mana balumilile okhulaama (iswala), ne bayinie eshihanwa shia Izaka, baba bali abana benyu mudini. Ne khwinoosilinjia tsinyaali tsiefu abandu abamanya."
  9,12,"Ne nibafunaka ebitsubo biabu nibamalile okhulaka mana banyeka idini, yire abemilisi bobukhayi. Toto ebitsubo biabu bibula obukhala (khubo) tawe, bakhababario banyola okhulekha."
  9,13,"Koo, shimulakhupana nende Abandu bafunaka indakano ne nibasuubila muno okhurusia Omurumwa, nabo nibo babaranjilila enywe oburasi olwokhuranga? Koo mubaritsanga? Nyasaye niye wamukhoyeshele okhuria butswa toto nimuli Abasuubili."